overview:
Henry Suh is a sales&marketing person turned programmer. Prior deciding to change his career, he has been working for a Swiss-based skycruise company. His keen interest in web technology since commercial high school let him to decide to change his career sooner or later.

Henry attended some web programming courses and applied the skills in his circle of acquaintances first and expanded to other clients via freelancer platform oDesk where he is currently still active.

Now, he decided to earn a degree in computer science and is a prospective computer science student at Lucerne School of Engineering and Architecture.
